    "summary": "Notion exposes a REST Notion API at `https://api.notion.com`, a separate REST Admin API at `https://api.notion.com/admin`, a hosted MCP server at `https://mcp.notion.com/mcp` (plus SSE), and the `ntn` CLI; all require authentication via Notion-issued tokens or OAuth.",
