        "setup": "In the [Developer portal](https://www.notion.so/developers), create a personal access token, choose its workspace and capabilities (`Notion API` and/or `Workers`), then copy the token. Workspace admins can control PAT creation from **Settings & members → Connections**. For CLI use, export it as `NOTION_API_TOKEN`.",
